<div class=" drizzle-o-Layout__section-header">
  <h1 class="drizzle-b-h1">Design Principles</h1>
</div>

<div class="drizzle-o-Layout-content drizzle-b-LongFormText">
  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <p>
      Our design principles are shared guidelines that capture the essence of what great design means to our company and
      advice on how to achieve it.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <div class="sprk-o-Flag sprk-o-Flag--stacked">
      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__figure">
        <svg height="75" viewBox="0 0 246.21 219.77">
          <use xlink:href="#flashlight" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__body">
        <h2 class="drizzle-b-h2">
          Clarity
        </h2>
        <p>
          Help eliminate ambiguity and enable users to see, understand and act with confidence. Keep the user focused on
          their goal without distraction.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <div class="sprk-o-Flag sprk-o-Flag--stacked">
      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__figure">
        <svg height="75" viewBox="0 0 246.21 219.77">
          <use xlink:href="#squares" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__body">
        <h2 class="drizzle-b-h2">
          Consistency
        </h2>
        <p>
          Create familiarity &amp; strengthen intuition by applying the same solution to the same problem. Use consistent
          language, patterns and components across the experience to make it easier for clients to get stuff done.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <div class="sprk-o-Flag sprk-o-Flag--stacked">
      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__figure">
        <svg height="75" viewBox="0 0 220.63 197.62">
          <use xlink:href="#leaves" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__body">
        <h2 class="drizzle-b-h2">
          Beauty
        </h2>
        <p>
          Every aesthetic design decision - from how we design components, to illustrations, and choices about color -
          should be purposeful. Build trust and further imbue confidence with an experience that appears and interacts
          beautifully.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <div class="sprk-o-Flag sprk-o-Flag--stacked">
      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__figure">
        <svg height="75" viewBox="0 0 220.63 197.62">
          <use xlink:href="#heart" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__body">
        <h2 class="drizzle-b-h2">
          Inclusive
        </h2>
        <p>
          Be inclusive, legible and as readable as possible across the experience. Thoughtfully serve the needs of all
          people.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <div class="sprk-o-Flag sprk-o-Flag--stacked">
      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__figure">
        <svg height="75" viewBox="0 0 220.63 197.62">
          <use xlink:href="#sparkler" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__body">
        <h2 class="drizzle-b-h2">
          Delight
        </h2>
        <p>
          With all other principles accounted for, enhance the user's experience through thoughtful craftsmanship and elegant
          micro interactions and transitions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
